'''Slip 45-J''' was a landing bay located in [[Kwilaan Starport/Legends|Kwilaan Starport]] in the [[City/Legends|city]] of [[Keren/Legends|Keren]] on the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] of [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]]. In [[23 BBY/Legends|23 BBY]], [[Captain/Legends|Captain]] [[Calquad Dominé]] refused to move [[Gender/Legends|his]] [[Mining/Legends|mining]] [[Transport/Legends|transport]], ''[[Pickaxe]]'' from this slip, forcing an arriving [[Refugee/Legends|refugee]] transport to divert to [[Theed/Legends|Theed]].<ref name="NMCPP">{{HoloNetNewsWeb|53|regional/13425_1.html|Naboo Miners Clog Ports in Protest}}</ref>

